9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Dragon: The Bruce Lee Story | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"This film is a glimpse into the life, love and the unconquerable spirit of the legendary Bruce Lee. From a childhood of rigorous martial arts training, Lee realizes his dream of opening his own kung-fu school in America. Before long, he is discovered by a Hollywood producer and begins a meteoric rise to fame and an all too short reign as one the most charismatic action heroes in cinema history."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/102720/dragon-the-bruce-lee-story"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Dragon: The Bruce Lee Story"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"This film is a glimpse into the life, love and the unconquerable spirit of the legendary Bruce Lee. From a childhood of rigorous martial arts training, Lee realizes his dream of opening his own kung-fu school in America. Before long, he is discovered by a Hollywood producer and begins a meteoric rise to fame and an all too short reign as one the most charismatic action heroes in cinema history."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/102720/dragon-the-bruce-lee-story"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lxhsdC8wuGgQf0gKCt8wyHHxGcQ.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Dragon: The Bruce Lee Story"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"This film is a glimpse into the life, love and the unconquerable spirit of the legendary Bruce Lee. 